        <section>
    	    <title>Available Mailing Lists</title>
	    <p>There are currently the following mailing lists:</p>
	    <ul>
		<li>ufmcontrol-users</li>
		<li>ufmcontrol-devel</li>
		<li>ufmcontrol-announce</li>
		<li>ufmcontrol-cvs</li>
	    </ul>
	    <p>To subscribe to a list, send an email, having subject or body of
	       the message the word <em>subscribe</em>, respectively to:</p>
	    <ul>
		<li><link href="mailto:ufmcontrol-users-request&amp;#64;lists.sourceforge.net">ufmcontrol-users-request at lists.sourceforge.net</link></li>
		<li><link href="mailto:ufmcontrol-devel-request&amp;#64lists.sourceforge.net">ufmcontrol-devel-request at lists.sourceforge.net</link></li>
		<li><link href="mailto:ufmcontrol-announce-request&amp;#64lists.sourceforge.net">ufmcontrol-announce-request at lists.sourceforge.net</link></li>
		<li><link href="mailto:ufmcontrol-cvs-request&amp;#64lists.sourceforge.net">ufmcontrol-cvs-request at lists.sourceforge.net</link></li>
	    </ul>
	    <p>(To unsubscribe yourself from a list, change the word
	       <em>subscribe</em> with <em>unsubscribe</em>)</p>
	</section>
    </body>
